item.title: CVE-2023-2326|2024-08-02T06:19:14.883Z -- unknown -- gravity%20forms%20google%20sheet%20connector
item.description: The Gravity Forms Google Sheet Connector WordPress plugin before 1.3.5, gsheetconnector-gravityforms-pro WordPress plugin through 1.3.5 does not have CSRF check when updating its Access Code, which could allow attackers to make logged in admin change the access code to an arbitrary one via a CSRF attack
